title: Was a Good Trend of Mine 3/13: Friday the 13th, CEO, Coronapocalypse, Andrew Gillum
itunes:title: Was a Good Trend of Mine 3/13: Friday the 13th, CEO, Coronapocalypse, Andrew Gillum
description:
On this edition of Was a Good Trend of Mine Jack and Miles discuss Friday the 13th trending (because that is today), CEOs are on blast to see how they react to Coronavirus as well as why certain CEOs are rallying around Trump, people are sharing info re: Corona for health, safety, and mental comfort, and Andrew Gillum was found with drugs and someone who had OD’d (no fatalities).
